snippet.title: Fujita Maiko (藤田麻衣子) - Nee (ねぇ)
snippet.description:
OP song of the anime Hiiro no Kakera. 

Note: If anyone is wondering what Nee (ねぇ) means, its simply "Hey". =)

I'll see if I can get the music video for this uploaded as well once my limited edition CD arrives. Do support Fujita Maiko by buying her CDs! 

Her Limited edition CD: http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B006YR3WJ4/

PS: You can also grab a DVD of her early summer live concert in Shibuya CC Lemon Hall (2011/6/11): http://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/B007H86BXI/

Remember folks! Do your bid to support this amazing artist!

snippet.title: Fujita Maiko (藤田麻衣子) - Hanabi (花火)
snippet.description:
Naitemo Naitemo (泣いても 泣いても), Hanabi (花火) single

Lyrics:
カランコロン　カランコロン
下駄の音
水たまり　団扇　六人
出掛けた夏の夜

君は白い浴衣　髪飾り
話し掛けられるたびに
君を上手く見れず

静かだった空に
一つ響いた音に
人々は足早になる

人込み　河川敷
黄色い花火が広がる空の下
振り返るたび君を探す

水風船や金魚すくいや
飛び交う大きな声に
屋台が続く道

いつもと違う町
いつもと違う夜
ふと変われそうな気がした

すれ違う人に
君が押し流されてしまわぬように
話し掛けて隣を歩く

この花火の夜
思い出にだけして
終わらせたくない
夏が行く前に

人込み　河川敷
真っ赤な花火が広がる空の下
君の手を握り走り出す 

\\Romajii || English//

KARAN KORON KARAN KORON
Geta no oto
Mizutamari Uchiwa Roku nin
Dekaketa natsu no yoru

Click Clonk Click Clonk
The sound of geta.
Puddles. Fans. 6 people.
We went out on that summer night.

Kimi wa shiroi yukata Kamikazari
Hanashi kakerareru tabi ni
Kimi wo umaku mirezu

You wore a white yukata and had a hair decoration.
As I spoke to you,
I couldn't see you very well.

Shizuka datta sora ni
Hitotsu hibiita oto ni
Hitobito wa ashibaya ni naru

In the sky that was quiet,
When a single sound echoed,
The people's feet move faster.

Hitogomi Kasenjiki
Kiiroi hanabi ga hirogaru sora no shita
Furikaeru tabi kimi wo sagasu

A crowd on the river bed
Below a sky filled with the spreading yellow fireworks.
When I turn around, I look for you.

Mizu fuusen ya kingyo sukui ya
Tobikau ookina koe ni
Yatai ga tsuzuku michi

There are water balloon yo-yos and goldfish scooping
On the path of stalls that continues on,
Jubilant voices calling out.

Itsumo to chigau machi
Itsumo to chigau yoru
Futo kawaresou na ki ga shita

A town different from usual.
A night different from usual.
I felt like it could change at any moment.

Surechigau hito ni
Kimi ga oshinagasarete shimawanu you ni
Hanashi kakete tonari wo aruku

In the crowds of people we pass by,
I talk to you as we walk side by side
So you don't get dragged away in the flow.

Kono hanabi no yoru
Omoide ni dake shite
Owarasetakunai
Natsu ga yuku mae ni

On this night of fireworks,
I don't want it to end
As just a memory
Before summer ends.

Hitogomi Kasenjiki
Makkana hanabi ga hirogaru sora no shita
Kimi no te wo nigiri hashiri dasu

A crowd on the river bed
Below a sky filled with the spreading pure red fireworks
I grab your hand and start to run.


Translated and transliterated by mewpudding101
http://mewpudding101.wordpress.com/

snippet.description:
11th track from her Mou Ichido album

Lyrics:
発車のベルに背中を押されて
Hassha no beru ni senaka o osa rete
乗り込んだ車両
Norikonda sharyō
ゆっくりと景色が流れ始めた
Yukkuri to keshiki ga nagare hajimeta

手渡されてた袋を開けると
Tewatasa re teta fukuro o akeruto
三つのおにぎり
Mittsu no onigiri
いいのに　もう　胸が詰まるよ
Iinoni mō mune ga tsumaru yo

握ってくれている姿とがんばれの声
Nigitte kurete iru sugata to ganbare no koe
聞こえた気がした
Kikoeta ki ga shita
気持ちが温かすぎて
Kimochi ga atataka sugite
涙が溢れるよ
Namida ga afureru yo

さよならがあるから
Sayonara ga arukara
また会いたくなるんだね
Mata aitaku naru da ne
淋しさを知って私を強くなる
Sabishi-sa o shitte watashi wa tsuyoku naru
そう思わなきゃ今は
Sō omowanakya ima wa
まだ淋しさに負けそうで
Mada sabishi-sa ni make-sōde
見えない明日　迷いながら
Mienai ashita mayoinagara
一人歩き出した
Hito aruki dashita

「今度帰るから」いつも言いながら
`Kondo kaerukara' itsumo iinagara
会えずに時間は過ぎていくよ
Aezu ni jikan wa sugite iku yo
元気にしてるの?
Genki ni shi teru no?

よく蝉を捕った神社
Yoku semi o totta jinja
秘密の隠れ家
Himitsu no kakureru 
長い通学路　あの薄紫の花は
Nagai tsūgaku-ro ano usumurasaki no hana wa
まだ咲いているかな
Mada saite iru ka na

長く間をあけて帰る
Nagaku ma o akete kaeru
身勝手な私を
Migattena watashi o
変わらない笑顔で
Kawaranai egao de
迎えてくれる
Mukaete kureru
その優しさにずっと
Sono yasashi-sa ni zutto
支えられてきたんだね
Sasae rarete kita da ne
大切な人たちがいる町を
Taisetsuna hito-tachi ga iru machi o
いつも忘れてないよ
Itsumo wasure tenai yo

さよならがあるから
Sayonara ga arukara
また会える嬉しさがある
Mata aeru ureshi-sa ga aru
離れるからこそわかる
Hanarerukara koso wakaru
そばにいられた幸せ
Soba ni i rareta shiawase

一番大事なのは物でもお金でもない
Ichiban daijina no wa mono de mo okane de mo nai
ただそばにいて
Tada soba ni ite
一緒に過ごせる時間
Issho ni sugoseru jikan
ただ元気でいて
Tada genkide ite
それが一番の願い
Sore ga ichiban no negai
また会えるから
Mata aerukara
がんばれるんだよ
Ganbareru nda yo
笑顔でいるよ
Egao de iru yo

胸を張って歩いていくよ
Mune o hatte aruite uku yo

snippet.title: Fujita Maiko (藤田麻衣子) - Kimi Ga te wo Nobasu Saki Ni (君が手を伸ばす先に)
snippet.description:
1st track from her Hiro no Kakera ~Best Album~

Lyrics:
Tsumetai kouki na yozora wo tsutsunde
The icy air covered the night sky,
Ame ga yuki no naru
the rain turned into hail and snow.
Doshite suki ni naru hito ni wa mou
Why did the person I love have someone
Aiteba hirota wo
beside him already?

Nozon demo munashi kono no dake na no ni ne
Even though I know that hoping to be with you is an illusion,
Aitai...
I still want to see you.

Yaru no osore owotto shite mo
Just how many times have I tried to forget about you?
Dame mitai do sureba ii
I can't do it, what should I do?
Kimi ni hitsu owotto sureta ii
I want to be someone that you need.
Kimi ga te wo nobasu saki ni
When you reached out with your hand,
Watashi ga inare tara
and I was the person in front of you,
Donna ni shiawase naro
oh, how blissful would that be.

Yasashiku sareru to na takuru shikunaru
The more gentle you are to be, the more painful it is.
Matta kitta aishiteru
I'm still hoping.

Sonna koto kurikaesu dake de doko ni wo
This kind of scenery just keeps repeating
Susurenai
With no development.

Ima wa kono kimochi dake de
With this emotion in my embrace,
Ganbareru te no hontou wa
I will work hard
Kimi ni dakeshimeraretai
But what I really want is to be embraced by you again.
Aisareru shiawase wo
To experience the happiness of being loved,
Kono te de kanjitai
I want to use my own two hands.
Donna ni shiawase naro
That would be so blissful.

Kimi ni hitsu owotto suretai
I want to be a person that you need.
Watashi ja ikenai no ka na
Can't it be me?

Narundo wasure owotto shite mo
Just how many times have I tried to forget about you?
Dame mitai do sureba ii
I can't do it, what should I do?
Kimi ni hitsu owotto suretai
I want to be someone that you need.
Kimi ga te wo nobasu saki ni
When you reached out with your hand,
Watashi ga iraretara
and I was the person in front of you,
Keshite sono te wo hanasenai
I will never let go (give up)
Watashi ga irareta nara
If I was standing in front of you.
Keshite hanasanai no ni
I will never leave you.

PS: I can't recall where I got the lyrics and translation from so apologies for using it~

Enjoy~

snippet.description:
Song: Futari no Kare
Lyrics Romaji:

aki no kaze ga hada o nadeta yoru
deatta toshiue no kare
naze ka wa wakaranai
nan demo hanasete  jikan o wasurete
misukasareteru you na
shisen ni mimi ga atsukunaru

igokochi no ii shizuka na kuuki no naka
me to me ga au shunkan
subete ga kuzureru
anata no yubi ga
watashi o hikiyoseru

kono hito wa kitto
zutto wakaranai hito
dakara shiritai to omou
wakaritai to negau
modokashii kanjou ni
watashi wa naite
kono hito o watashi wa suki da to
omoishirasareru

yasashii haru no hizashi no shita
deatta toshishita no kare
issho ni iru dake de
tonari de waraikaketekureru dake de
nandaka shiawase na
atatakai kimochi ni naru

doushite itsumo
sonna ni yasashii no
haritsumeta kimochi ga
yowakunaritai toki ni kagitte
tonari ni itekureru

sono hito wa itsumo
watashi o wakattekureru
jibun rashiku isasetekureru
kokoro sukuwareru kumori no nai egao o
kizutsuketakunai
kono hito o suki ni nareta nara
donna ni ii darou

aisareru hou ga
shiawase ni nareru tte
wakatteru no ni
kokoro ga iu koto o kikanai
kizutsuite mo watashi wa

kono hito wa kitto
zutto wakaranai hito
dakara shiritai to omou
wakaritai to negau
modokashii kanjou ni
watashi wa naite
kono hito o watashi wa suki da to
omoishirasareru

futari no kare
dochira mo watashi ni wa taisetsu na hito

demo watashi wa
aishite wa kurenai hito o erabu no

English:

on a night when the autumn wind caressed my skin
that was when i met him, the older boy
i don't know why
but i could talk to him for hours end about anything
his gaze seemed to look right through me
it made my ears grow hot

in that cozy and quiet atmosphere
the moment our eyes meet
everything falls apart
your fingers
draw me close into you

this person must be
someone i've never known
that's why i long to know him
i want to understand him
this tantalizing feeling
it makes me cry
it causes me to realize
that i love him

under the gentle light of spring
that was when i met him, the younger boy
just being together with him
just having him next to me flashing me his smile
it sort of gives me
a warm and happy feeling

why must you
always be so kind?
just when i want to release
my bottled-up feelings
you are there for me

this person
has always understood me
he lets me be myself
that sunny smile of his brightened up my heart
i don't want it to falter
if i fell for him
imagine how wonderful it would be

i would be happier
to be loved
i know
but my heart won't listen
even if it pains me, i...

this person must be
someone i've never known
that's why i long to know him
i want to understand him
this tantalizing feeling
it makes me cry
it causes me to realize
that i love him

two boys
both are dear to me

but i
i chose the one who would not return my love
